and the second specifies the covariant derivative to be integrated by parts.\n\
\nFor example, the equation of motion, stress tensors and trace of free \
scalar are"
}], "Text",ExpressionUUID->"7c1ef0e4-c1cc-4639-a695-0f5dfa4fa2c0"],

